Cost-effectiveness of embryo transfer strategies: a decision analytic model 
using long-term costs and consequences of singletons and multiples born as a 
consequence of IVF.

van Heesch MM(1), van Asselt AD(2)(3), Evers JL(4)(5), van der Hoeven MA(6), 
Dumoulin JC(4)(5), van Beijsterveldt CE(7), Bonsel GJ(8)(9), Dykgraaf RH(10), 
van Goudoever JB(11)(12), Koopman-Esseboom C(13), Nelen WL(14), Steiner K(15), 
Tamminga P(16), Tonch N(17), Torrance HL(18), Dirksen CD(19).

Author information:
